{"tid":1309192,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"花旗香港取消 citibanking / citi priority 低額結餘月費","createTime":"2019-07-12T06:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T03:25:40.000Z","uid":44569,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"98386e29301776fb8d4d724a88d9d1cbd0d16cf5","tid":1309192,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:03:10.000Z","msg":"花旗香港發出新聞稿指，將取消Citibanking理財及Citi Priority的低額結餘服務月費，此前Citibanking理財用戶若每日平均總結餘低於1萬元，將被收取60元服務月費；Citi Priority用戶若每日平均總結餘低於50萬，服務月費將為120元。至於針對高端客戶的Citigold 、花旗私人客戶業務及國際個人銀行服務，每日平均總結餘要求及服務月費則維持不變。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐於上月底宣布豁免部分個人戶口的最低結餘月費，至今已有至少8間銀行跟隨，包括中銀香港（2388）、渣打、恒生銀行（0011）、東亞（0023）、工銀亞洲、大新銀行、華僑永亨銀行及花旗銀行。"},{"pid":"7fcb745ef103060df12ab14ea49d280b82b2fa8a","tid":1309192,"uid":109263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:05:02.000Z","msg":"補刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4c9e3f9a0b4e8a1ac6c6f64d86a76f52c7a834","tid":1309192,"uid":39122,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:07:05.000Z","msg":"其實至少兩年前開始，佢已經開始邀請啲客上 CitiPriority，講到明結餘唔夠都唔收服務費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e821b8faae7ba8071f26b2dad188c78d6f80fa2","tid":1309192,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:24:17.000Z","msg":"如果佢 priority 都免低結存費<br />\n咁就可以玩佢個出糧戶口 promo"},{"pid":"3a17253f18b2b5dac8343b67719881b4f99ddd67","tid":1309192,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:27:23.000Z","msg":"姐係放一舊錢落去 再拎返出黎都開到？"},{"pid":"824db883175ebabf1ae0e1afd60590c24d1ef401","tid":1309192,"uid":56732,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:42:18.000Z","msg":"開左/打算開離岸美國券商既巴打有福了<br />\nCiti Priority電匯免費<br />\n慳返唔少手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f36c9725f713c167287923c467a344f5d03e6a","tid":1309192,"uid":118997,"like":1,"disl